#Text=Mover president says : " Have a seat , I 'm just working on a cure for the common cold .
#Text=I need your help to stop the Evil Unalaq .
#Text=" Mover president says : " Did you say " help " ?
#Text=If there is one thing I love doing , it 's helping people .
#Text=" Buttercup Raiko says : " The seal lion seemed a bit far fetched , but the portrayal of this president is right on the money .
#Text=" Asami says : " I think this is your best mover yet .
#Text=" Bolin says : " I just wish Mako was here to see it .
#Text=" Lu says : " Mmm .
#Text=I like to eat the top of the Varri - cake first .
#Text=" Gang says : " I just try to shove the whole thing in my mouth at once .
#Text=" Lu says : " I love our job .
#Text=" Nuktuk says : " Northern Water Tribe automatons !
#Text=No !
#Text=" Automatons says : " Bee bow bop , Nuktuk can not stop Unalaq , must destroy Nuktuk .
#Text=" Nuktuk says : " Haha !
#Text=Arhg !
#Text=Looks like you forgot that water , and automatons , do n't mix .
#Text=" Automatons says : " Bee bow bop , oh no , circuits no working .
#Text=" Nuktuk says : " Hahaho !
#Text=We did it !
#Text=But wait , where 's Juji ?
